name: vectorArt:theGreatest
description:
This is a piece I've made in gratitude for my top 24 collectors. This NFT won't be on sale on primary market.
If you have received one edition, it means you are one of the 24 collectors who had collected more pieces I've done. I want to thank you for supporting my art, and helping me to live of doing this stuff that I love to do.
I hope you like it.
Delcarmat.
